      <title>Obama administration reportedly planning more deportation raids</title>

      <title>Trump says Washington Post owner Bezos has 'huge antitrust problem'</title>

      <title>Obama administration tells public schools to let transgender students use bathrooms of their choice</title>
      <description>The Obama administration is expected to release a letter telling every public school district in the country to allow transgender students to use the bathrooms that match their gender identity, The New York Times reported late Thursday.<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/foxnews/politics/~4/sZEsCQL9Zbk" height="1" width="1" alt=""/></description>

      <title>New email release shows Clinton chose not to use secure phone line, acknowledged Blackberry risk</title>
      <description>A new set of State Department documents released Thursday by the watchdog group Judicial Watch reveal then-Secretary of State Hillary Clinton made the choice not to use a secure phone line amid a technical problem and acknowledged the risk of using a private Blackberry phone.<img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/foxnews/politics/~4/n2_mxFiZhQM" height="1" width="1" alt=""/></description>

      <title>New Senate bill requires VA kitchen health inspections after roach problems</title>
